# Only the Play screenshots — NOT the whole metadata dir. The listing text and
# changelogs under it are release-critical (they are what users read in the
# store) and belong in review, exactly like the tracked fastlane/metadata-mac.
# Ignoring all of it is why changelogs/3002.txt was never in git.
fastlane/metadata/**/images/

